Class LinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
Lists.LinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held in this collection
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class LinkedList<T> extends Object implements ListADT<T>
LinkedList represents a linked implementation of a list.
